        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "The engine API is the internal channel each CL uses to drive its EL. **Not an external contract** - it is an internal-dependency SLO. The two pairs report the SLI under different metric names (client diversity): the **validating pair** (teku to besu) uses outcome=success, the **archive pair** (lighthouse to geth) uses payload status=valid."
